12
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:06,950
But exactly how we characterise that isn&#39;t completely clear yet.

13
00:01:06,950 --> 00:01:11,140
Language development in babies is a really lively area of research.

14
00:01:11,140 --> 00:01:14,130
Known as developmental psycholinguistics.

15
00:01:14,130 --> 00:01:20,000
I just want to set the stage by pointing out that... language is specific to human beings.

16
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,470
Now, let&#39;s not confuse communication with language.

17
00:01:24,470 --> 00:01:30,060
